des: "Nice and easy healthy. Blend then put it in your freezer during dinner and have the spread for the sandwich ready for dessert!"
ins:
Combine milk, banana, ice cubes, and sugar in a blender; blend until smooth. Pour into a freezer-safe container.
Freeze banana ice cream until firm, about 30 minutes.
Spread ice cream onto 10 graham crackers; top each with another graham cracker to create a sandwich.
